+# Applying this archive to the upstream repository
+
+The sandbox used to build this archive could not perform a full `git clone` of GitHub, so this package contains the complete additive local-cluster implementation plus an application script.
+
+From a normal development machine:
+
+```bash
+git clone https://github.com/dywongcloud/rusternetes.git
+cd rusternetes
+/path/to/rusternetes-local-platform/APPLY_TO_UPSTREAM.sh "$PWD"
+cargo fmt --all -- --check
+cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings
+cargo test --workspace
+cargo install --path crates/rusternetes-cli
+```
+
+The script copies all added files and patches `Cargo.toml`, `Makefile`, and `README.md` without replacing existing Rūsternetes component crates.
